reviews.text: You can eat very good Indian food. I recommend to anyone who lives this style
The food is really good and not that expensive! We ate here multiple times and we were never let down. The ambience is great, and the waiters are very kind.
We went for a lunch buffet on a Groupon offer. Loved the food and the service was excellent. Atmosphere was calm and inviting. Strongly recommend. Not sure what the full pricing is.
Hundred tewnty for an Indian buffet dining, value for money. Old restaurant but cozy. Good food. Wanna to try their dinner.
I've been coming to this place for years. The food and service has always been great.
